install rubygems:

sudo apt-get install rubygems1.8

ruby headers (required for building the ruby gem):

sudo apt-get install ruby1.8-dev

install id3lib support:

sudo aptitude install libid3-dev

sudo gem install id3lib-ruby

sudo gem install rspec


sudo apt-get install zlib1g-dev


sudo gem install ruby-mp3info

we use mp3info because it properly supports character sets when reading/writing tags
